Run the app as follows:

Non-distibuted OCR on x86:
OCR_TYPE=x86 make install

To build and run:
OCR_TYPE=x86 make run

For distributed OCR on x86:
OCR_TYPE=x86-mpi make install

To build and run:
OCR_TYPE=x86-mpi make run

The problem size is set to 5x5x5 lattice cells. It is specified in the corresponding makefiles via "WORKLOAD_ARGS" variable as "WORKLOAD_ARGS ?= -x 5 -y 5 -z 5".
